<br>
To emphasize a point someone made earlier, there is a huge gap between the good weapons and the uber weapons for warriors. Much like there's a huge gap in our lives where we gain no new abilities (36-50)... both those aspects just creates a void of something to work for. So, for those 15 levels, we are nothing but slaves to the xp grind (coincidentally, a skid row pun). OK OK... to the point, beyond getting more warrior only weapons, I'd have valued more abilities to work for when I was grinding through level 36-50.<br>
<br>
